Resource Profile: FR PractitionerRole Document

Official URL: https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-practitionerRole-document Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2026-01-19 Computable Name: FRPractitionerRoleDocument

Ce profil représente les professionnels de santé et leurs rôles dans le cadre d’un document médical.

Utilisations:

  • Utiliser ce Profil: FR Bundle Document
  • Référer à ce Profil: Observation - FR Observation Vital Signs Panel Document, FR Actor Extension, FR Composition Document, Condition - FR Condition Document... Show 29 more, DeviceRequest - FR Device request Document, DeviceUseStatement - FR Device Use Statement Document, DiagnosticReport - FR Diagnostic Report BIO chapter Document, DiagnosticReport - FR Diagnostic Report Document, DiagnosticReport - FR Diagnostic Report Imaging Document, FR Encounter Care Document, FamilyMemberHistory - FR Family Member History Document, Immunization - FR Immunization Document, Media - FR Media Document, MedicationRequest - FR Medication Request Document, Observation - FR Observation Administration Blood Derivatives Document, Observation - FR Observation Antenatal Testing And Surveillance Battery Document, Observation - FR Blood Product Transfusion Document, Observation - FR Observation Contra Indications Document, Observation - FR Observation Laboratory Report Results Document, Observation - FR Observation Medical Summary Document, Observation - FR Observation Microorganism Detection Document, Observation - FR Observation Pregnancy Document, Observation - FR Observation Radiation Exposure Document, Observation - FR Observation Result Document, Observation - FR Observation Survey Document, Observation - FR Observation Transfusion Accidents Document, Observation - FR Observation Vital Signs Document, Observation - FR Observation Work Related Accident Document, FR Performer Event Extension, Procedure - FR Procedure Act Document, Procedure - FR Procedure Imaging Document, Specimen - FR Specimen Document and Task - FR Task Patient Transport Document
